collections.name: Purple Frens
collections.description: Purple Frens began as a vision to unite creativity, utility, and community on the blockchain. Inspired by the purple ecosystem of Monad, we’ve designed a collection of 1,111 unique NFTs that blend art, meme culture and community spirit. The Purple Frens NFTs acts as staking nodes in the Monad Pad ecosystem, with various benefits. This testnet collection serves as an early glimpse into the world of Purple Frens, but it’s not the final version, our mainnet collection will feature an expanded set of traits and surprises. Stay tuned for the full experience!

collections.name: Molandaks
collections.description: Molandaks is a community-driven NFT collection featuring 5,000 unique Molandak characters. It’s launching as a free mint on the Monad blockchain and is created with the blessing of the original Molandak creator. Molandaks aim to foster an inclusive and vibrant ecosystem that celebrates art, culture, and community collaboration.
